Class Packet

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.Packet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Packet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

    Packet Class used for sending information between Server and Client

    This Class contains a static reference to the strings to be sent as a representation of the operation this Packet was created to convey.
